{"tha-ap17:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap17:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap17:0.3":"5 Pilindavacchattheraapadana ","tha-ap17:1.1":"“Nibbute lokanathamhi, ","tha-ap17:1.2":"sumedhe aggapuggale; ","tha-ap17:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap17:1.4":"thupapujam akasaham. ","tha-ap17:2.1":"Ye ca khinasava tattha, ","tha-ap17:2.2":"chalabhinna mahiddhika; ","tha-ap17:2.3":"Teham tattha samanetva, ","tha-ap17:2.4":"sanghabhattam akasaham. ","tha-ap17:3.1":"Sumedhassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap17:3.2":"upatthako tada ahu; ","tha-ap17:3.3":"Sumedho nama namena, ","tha-ap17:3.4":"anumodittha so tada. ","tha-ap17:4.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap17:4.2":"vimanam upapajjaham; ","tha-ap17:4.3":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap17:4.4":"accharayo ramimsu me. ","tha-ap17:5.1":"Mameva anuvattanti, ","tha-ap17:5.2":"sabbakamehi ta sada; ","tha-ap17:5.3":"Anne deve abhibhomi, ","tha-ap17:5.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap17:6.1":"Pancavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap17:6.2":"varuno nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap17:6.3":"Visuddhabhojano asim, ","tha-ap17:6.4":"cakkavatti aham tada. ","tha-ap17:7.1":"Na te bijam pavapanti, ","tha-ap17:7.2":"napi niyanti nangala; ","tha-ap17:7.3":"Akatthapakimam salim, ","tha-ap17:7.4":"paribhunjanti manusa. ","tha-ap17:8.1":"Tattha rajjam karitvana, ","tha-ap17:8.2":"devattam puna gacchaham; ","tha-ap17:8.3":"Tadapi edisa mayham, ","tha-ap17:8.4":"nibbatta bhogasampada. ","tha-ap17:9.1":"Na mam mitta amitta va, ","tha-ap17:9.2":"himsanti sabbapanino; ","tha-ap17:9.3":"Sabbesampi piyo homi, ","tha-ap17:9.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap17:10.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap17:10.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap17:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap17:10.4":"gandhalepassidam phalam. ","tha-ap17:11.1":"Imasmim bhaddake kappe, ","tha-ap17:11.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap17:11.3":"Mahanubhavo rajaham, ","tha-ap17:11.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap17:12.1":"Soham pancasu silesu, ","tha-ap17:12.2":"thapetva janatam bahum; ","tha-ap17:12.3":"Papetva sugatimyeva, ","tha-ap17:12.4":"devatanam piyo ahum. ","tha-ap17:13.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap17:13.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap17:13.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap17:13.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap17:14.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pilindavaccho thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap17:15.1":"Pilindavacchattherassapadanam pancamam. "}